controllers

Class GUISender

  • java.lang.Object
    • hypeerweb.broadcast.SendVisitor
      • controllers.GUISender
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Visitor

    public class GUISender
extends SendVisitor
    Sends a message from the start node (the first node to receive this visitor) the indicated target node. As it traverses intermediate nodes it prints trace messages to the "TraceInformation" section of the GUI. When it gets to the target, it prints the target's webId and the message. 
                    Domain: None
